    questions: ['Describe a person who has had a positive influence on your life.'],
    examples: [{ simple: 'My teacher influenced me to study harder.', band7: 'My high school English teacher, Ms. Zhang, has had a profound influence on me. She not only taught me the language but also encouraged me to think critically and express my opinions confidently. Her passion for teaching and genuine care for every student inspired me to pursue a career in education myself.' }],
    part2Example: { simple: 'I want to talk about my mother. She is very kind and hardworking. She always helps me when I have problems.', band7: 'I\'d like to talk about my mother, who has been the most influential person in my life. She\'s an incredibly resilient woman who raised two children while running her own small business. What strikes me most about her is her unwavering optimism — no matter how difficult things got, she always found a way to stay positive. Growing up, I watched her work long hours, yet she never complained and always made time for us. Her determination taught me that success comes from persistence, and her kindness showed me the importance of giving back to the community. I truly believe that everything I\'ve achieved is, in large part, thanks to the values she instilled in me.' },
