    examples: [{ simple: 'I want to visit Japan because I like Japanese food.', band7: 'A place that\'s been on my bucket list for years is Iceland — I\'m fascinated by its dramatic volcanic landscapes and the chance to see the Northern Lights.' }],
    part2Example: { simple: 'I want to visit Paris because it is a famous city. I want to see the Eiffel Tower and eat French food.', band7: 'A destination I\'ve always dreamed of visiting is New Zealand. I\'ve seen countless documentaries and travel blogs about its stunning natural beauty — from the fjords of Milford Sound to the geothermal wonders of Rotorua. What appeals to me most is the incredible diversity of landscapes packed into a relatively small country: you can go from pristine beaches to alpine mountains within a few hours\' drive. I\'m also a big fan of outdoor activities, so I\'d love to try the hiking trails, especially the Tongariro Alpine Crossing, which is supposed to be one of the best day hikes in the world. Beyond the scenery, I\'m curious about the Maori culture and would like to experience a traditional hangi feast. I think New Zealand represents the kind of untouched natural beauty that\'s becoming increasingly rare, and I want to see it while it\'s still preserved.' },
