    examples: [{ simple: 'I went to my friend\'s birthday party last month.', band7: 'One celebration that stands out was my best friend\'s surprise 30th birthday party, which was organized by his wife at a rooftop restaurant overlooking the city skyline.' }],
    part2Example: { simple: 'I went to a wedding party last year. It was fun. There was good food and dancing.', band7: 'I\'d like to describe the Spring Festival celebration I experienced at my grandparents\' village when I was about twelve. It was the most vivid and joyful celebration I can remember. The whole village came alive in the days leading up to the New Year — every family was busy cleaning, decorating, and preparing traditional dishes. On New Year\'s Eve, three generations of our family gathered around a massive round table for the reunion dinner. My grandmother had spent days preparing her signature braised fish and dumplings. After dinner, the children set off firecrackers in the courtyard while the adults played cards and shared stories. The next morning, we visited neighbors with gifts and received red envelopes in return. What made it so special was the sense of community and continuity — knowing that these same traditions had been observed for generations. It was a powerful reminder of the importance of family and cultural heritage.' },
