    questions: ['Describe your favorite room in your home.'],
    examples: [{ simple: 'My bedroom is my favorite room because it is quiet.', band7: 'My favorite room is the small study I\'ve set up in the corner of our apartment — it\'s just big enough for a desk, a bookshelf, and a comfortable armchair by the window.' }],
    part2Example: { simple: 'My favorite room is my bedroom. It has a bed, a desk, and a window. I study and sleep there every day.', band7: 'I\'d like to describe my study, which is undoubtedly my favorite room in the house. It\'s a modest-sized room on the second floor with a large bay window that lets in plenty of natural light. The walls are painted a warm shade of sage green, which I find very calming. One entire wall is covered with floor-to-ceiling bookshelves filled with novels, textbooks, and travel souvenirs I\'ve collected over the years. The centerpiece is a solid oak desk that I found at a vintage market — it has a beautiful patina that gives it real character. I\'ve also added a few personal touches: a framed photo from my favorite trip, a small potted plant, and a vintage desk lamp that belonged to my grandfather. This room is where I do most of my work, but it\'s also my sanctuary — the place I go to read, think, and recharge. The combination of natural light, books, and meaningful objects makes it feel uniquely mine.' },
