    content: 'Describe a piece of technology you use regularly.',
    prompts: ['What it is', 'How long you have had it', 'What you use it for', 'How it has changed your life'],
    questions: ['Describe a piece of technology you use regularly.'],
    examples: [{ simple: 'I use my smartphone every day for calling and chatting.', band7: 'The piece of technology I rely on most is my e-reader — I\'ve had it for about two years, and it has completely transformed my reading habits.' }],
    part2Example: { simple: 'I use my laptop every day. I got it two years ago. I use it for work and study. It is very useful.', band7: 'I\'d like to talk about my smart watch, which I\'ve been using for about a year now. It\'s a relatively simple model — not one of the high-end ones — but it has made a surprisingly big impact on my daily life. The main reason I bought it was to track my fitness. It monitors my steps, heart rate, and sleep patterns, and it gently reminds me to move if I\'ve been sitting for too long. Before I got it, I was quite sedentary — I\'d often spend eight hours at my desk without standing up. Now, I regularly hit my daily step goal and I\'ve become much more conscious of my activity levels. Beyond fitness, it\'s also incredibly convenient for quick tasks like checking notifications, setting timers, and even making contactless payments — all without having to pull out my phone. What I appreciate most is how it seamlessly integrates into my routine without being intrusive. It\'s a small device, but it has genuinely improved my health and productivity.' },
