    questions: ['Describe a famous person you would like to meet.'],
    examples: [{ simple: 'I admire Elon Musk because he is very innovative.', band7: 'Someone I deeply admire is Malala Yousafzai — her courage in standing up for girls\' education, even at great personal risk, is truly extraordinary.' }],
    part2Example: { simple: 'I want to meet Jack Ma. He is a famous businessman in China. He started Alibaba. I think he is very smart.', band7: 'I\'d like to talk about a famous person I\'d love to meet — the documentary filmmaker David Attenborough. He\'s been a household name for decades, known for his groundbreaking nature documentaries like Planet Earth and Blue Planet. What I admire most about him is not just his incredible knowledge of the natural world, but his ability to communicate complex environmental issues in a way that resonates with ordinary people. Even in his nineties, he continues to be a passionate advocate for environmental conservation. If I had the chance to meet him, I would ask him what gives him hope in the face of climate change, and what he believes individuals can do to make a real difference. I\'d also love to hear stories from his decades of traveling to the most remote corners of the planet. I think his life exemplifies how one person\'s dedication and storytelling ability can shift public consciousness on a global scale.' },
