    questions: ['Describe a quiet place where you like to spend time.'],
    examples: [{ simple: 'I like to go to a park near my home on weekends.', band7: 'My favorite quiet place is a small reading room on the top floor of the city library — it has floor-to-ceiling windows overlooking a garden and is almost always deserted.' }],
    part2Example: { simple: 'I like a cafe near my school. It is quiet. I go there to read books and drink coffee.', band7: 'I\'d like to describe a place that has become my personal sanctuary over the past year — a small botanical garden about 20 minutes\' walk from my apartment. It\'s tucked away behind a residential area, so most tourists don\'t know about it, which means it\'s wonderfully peaceful. The garden is divided into several sections: a bamboo grove, a pond with lotus flowers, and a rose garden that\'s spectacular in early summer. My favorite spot is a wooden bench under a large willow tree by the pond. I try to visit at least once a week, usually on Sunday mornings when it\'s least crowded. I bring a book or just sit and listen to the sounds of nature — birds singing, water rippling, leaves rustling in the breeze. In our fast-paced, screen-dominated world, having access to such a tranquil space is incredibly valuable. It helps me clear my mind, reduce stress, and return to my daily life feeling refreshed and recharged.' },
