    questions: ['Describe a colleague you enjoy working with.'],
    examples: [{ simple: 'My teammate is very helpful and friendly.', band7: 'The colleague I enjoy working with most is a senior frontend engineer on my team who has an incredible ability to break down complex technical problems into manageable pieces.' }],
    part2Example: { simple: 'I want to talk about my colleague Li Wei. He is a frontend developer like me. He is very smart and always helps me. I like working with him.', band7: 'I\'d like to describe a colleague I genuinely enjoy working with — a senior frontend architect on my team who I\'ve collaborated with for about three years. He\'s the kind of person who can look at a messy codebase and immediately identify the root cause of a performance issue. What impresses me most isn\'t just his technical expertise — though that\'s formidable — it\'s his patience and willingness to mentor others. Whenever I run into a tricky bug or need advice on system design, he never just gives me the answer. Instead, he asks the right questions to guide me toward the solution myself, which has helped me grow tremendously as a developer. Outside of work, he\'s also great company — we often grab lunch together and chat about everything from new JavaScript frameworks to our favorite hiking trails around Hangzhou. Working alongside someone who is both exceptionally skilled and genuinely kind has been one of the highlights of my career.' },
    relatedPart2Id: null, difficulty: 'medium', isCustom: false, isFavorite: false, createdAt: 0, updatedAt: 0,
